    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "# ReShade用に何千ものプリセットカラープリセットを収録したリポジトリ"
  },
  {
    "row": 15,
    "rowsha": "8OIiyBd80ZjijAiD6S40uxsv22gkgE2wNTJo4hGjO8U=",
    "originContent": "# A repository with thousands of predefined color presets for ReShade",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 16,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## **LUTとは何ですか？**"
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "4aO6waAOfxaDkOzmzidCBMaen35ONsp+Kxo0oCAX0WM=",
    "originContent": "## **What is a LUT?**",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "LUT（カラー・ルックアップ・テーブル）は、ReShadeをインストールできる任意のゲームで使える焼き込み済みのカラープリセットです。"
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "ZUrwpp7vEJI1z1G7Wrql50E5P16R0RnHQsSXBSwUAm8=",
    "originContent": "LUTs (Color Lookup Table) are baked color presets you can use in any game you can install ReShade to.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## **動作させるために何が必要ですか？**"
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "/0gqe0NF/sJQpx9dWeWkBCSFV/Gyh8/fM1HJdlQ+xWI=",
    "originContent": "## **What do I need to get it working?**",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "+ [ReShade](https://reshade.me)"
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "w1W6ILVtJSpWVTrC2ZL0y6pX8mymZaZXQTFparqBaOY=",
    "originContent": "+ [ReShade](https://reshade.me)",
    "translatedContent": "+ このリポジトリに付属する**_BaseLUT.fxh**ファイル"
  },
  {
    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "uuWgq0CNJeU0Iaq2Fs6SpELa6MI5t2CmFl6tfs7ILpI=",
    "originContent": "+ The **_BaseLUT.fxh** file that comes with this repository",
    "translatedContent": "+ デフォルトのReShadeインストールに含まれるファイル"
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "l2qvEHWDe+/VH3TZwjxTj/YJKaulH3EyTc0Xk6+96Oc=",
    "originContent": "+ Files that come with the default reshade installation.",
    "translatedContent": "  + **ReShade.fxh**"
  },
  {
    "row": 26,
    "rowsha": "H2ltJKvfVRawfXTwL0FudeKiHE+MuK0jcrIyO3/GTVM=",
    "originContent": "  + **ReShade.fxh**",
    "translatedContent": "  + **ReShadeUI.fxh**"
  },
  {
    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "+B+bhWpxaOEvKkk3jfIb49tuaOKTFFD+1NKVJjUtY9M=",
    "originContent": "  + **ReShadeUI.fxh**",
    "translatedContent": "+ ファイル名が一致する**.fx**および**.png**ファイル"
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "3MPqmReLVxdcHT/1UEmrbKeRgm67cFJpDTZZ6CuI6go=",
    "originContent": "+ The **.fx** and **.png** files with matching file names.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## **インストール方法**"
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "h8lIUoSfYAbfo5ee3jI65AOEDUHnIHcWVkxxbmh8mSQ=",
    "originContent": "## **Installation**",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "1. [リポジトリをダウンロード](https://github.com/TheGordinho/MLUT/archive/refs/heads/master.zip)します。"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "tDYEGHUhMF+H5FPal/cas7O6RSAiwKsDSZeLMID3Dhk=",
    "originContent": "1. [Download](https://github.com/TheGordinho/MLUT/archive/refs/heads/master.zip) the repository.",
    "translatedContent": "2. 使用したい**.fx**ファイル（全部である必要はなく、使いたいものだけ）をReShadeのインストールフォルダ内のShadersフォルダに移動します。"
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "+F7/oLhqi7C/A6XJ5bA3BEyys782ORwthzULtmtd68E=",
    "originContent": "2. Move the **.fx** files that you want (you don't need them all, just the ones you want) to the Shaders folder inside your reshade install folder.",
    "translatedContent": "3. 対応する**.png**ファイルをReShadeのインストールフォルダ内のTexturesフォルダに移動します。"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "mJvsjd7wtC8UfkctNu8jwhbuxdSh8sN7EHmmaaFlKwI=",
    "originContent": "3. Move the matching **.png** files to the Textures folder inside your reshade install folder.",
    "translatedContent": "4. 完了です！"
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "SZYNLXFSOcHDjhZt2kCJqwoTpleNwUcm1pBK87Eeg/k=",
    "originContent": "4. Done!",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
