  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "LWh5riXOTMsxfyy3NXa4Wp1+WtCziBlhDQnfawEfH/4=",
    "originContent": "You can mix and match as many luts as you want, but be aware that you will start to see heavy color banding with 2 or more LUTs active at the same time.",
    "translatedContent": "好きなだけ多くのLUTを組み合わせることができますが、2つ以上のLUTを同時に有効にすると強いカラーバンディングが発生し始めることに注意してください。"
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
